{"tid":2198789,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★香港房屋福利已經超越歐美國家！！！","createTime":"2020-09-11T15:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T04:38:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d34351b8d222869ea2ff15155c7daabcbf25d8d","tid":2198789,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">香港房屋福利已經超越被譽為福利國家的歐美國家</span><br />\n<br />\n根據經濟合作及發展組織（OECD 經合組織）二○一八年抽樣調查了經合組織21個成員國中超過22,000人，當中只有三分之一人（即33.33%）享有公共住屋服務。<br />\n香港統計處資料顯示香港目前有814,410個家庭居住於出租公屋，另外386,900個家庭居住於資助房屋，分別佔香港家庭30.79%及14.63%，佔香港家庭總數的45.42%，遠超於經合組織國家的33.33%！<br />\n<br />\n經合組織於二○一九年十二月十六日更新的HOUSING COSTS OVER INCOME（住屋消費與入息比率）提出，當住屋消費（包括租住或供房消費）超過40%可使用如下便定性為住屋消費超負荷，而香港出租公屋的租金只是入息限額的8.5-10.73%。<span class=\"xx-large\">香港的房屋福利已經超越歐美福利國家！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/onad/bkn/cnt/ad/20200910/ad-20200910174430735-0910_21011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fonad%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fad%2F20200910%2Fad-20200910174430735-0910_21011_001.html&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fmDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=c3fefab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/onad/bkn/cnt/ad/20200910/ad-20200910174430735-0910_21011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cf7a1ce535374cff226b419f999290b70be5303a","tid":2198789,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246a703af585f6f24bc0988209e6586b52f55a41","tid":2198789,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T15